- Hello? - Seol.

532
00:34:03,947 --> 00:34:06,077
This is Sang Mi, the part-timer at Riccardo.

533
00:34:06,177 --> 00:34:07,907
Oh, Sang Mi.

534
00:34:07,977 --> 00:34:11,217
Seol. I heard that you're a veterinarian, right?

535
00:34:11,307 --> 00:34:13,007
What's wrong? Did something happen?

536
00:34:13,577 --> 00:34:17,577
Mimi has been in so much pain all night.

537
00:34:19,277 --> 00:34:20,947
Please save Mimi's life.

538
00:34:23,877 --> 00:34:25,377
Sang Mi, where are you now?

539
00:34:26,547 --> 00:34:28,877
Yes, I know where it is. I'll see you in 30 minutes.

540
00:34:32,077 --> 00:34:34,577
Are you going to stay silent hoping that it'd blow over?

541
00:34:34,647 --> 00:34:37,107
It might blow up and hit you hard if you just leave it like this.

542
00:34:38,007 --> 00:34:39,007
I know.

543
00:34:39,777 --> 00:34:42,877
Tae Min's mom won't let it slide,

544
00:34:43,377 --> 00:34:46,807
and the media will pour out articles based on speculation.

545
00:34:47,107 --> 00:34:49,717
You know so well. And you still don't want to deal with the media?

546
00:34:49,777 --> 00:34:51,877
I'm going to think of it as my fate as a popular author...

547
00:34:51,877 --> 00:34:53,407
and let it slide.

548
00:34:53,547 --> 00:34:56,277
There were times when I thought I'd be willing to pay...

549
00:34:56,947 --> 00:34:59,977
a bigger price than this in order to become a famous author.

550
00:35:01,077 --> 00:35:02,147
I should endure it.

551
00:35:04,407 --> 00:35:06,147
Hey, stop maturing up.

552
00:35:06,147 --> 00:35:07,777
You're starting to become no fun.

553
00:35:10,217 --> 00:35:11,347
Anyway, you better get ready.

554
00:35:11,347 --> 00:35:12,847
Reporters will swarm around here.

555
00:35:12,907 --> 00:35:16,077
It'll probably be worse than when the stalker committed suicide.

556
00:35:16,147 --> 00:35:17,547
I know for a fact that it won't be easier.

557
00:35:18,877 --> 00:35:20,107
The stalker...

558
00:35:21,947 --> 00:35:23,217
It must've surprised you a lot.

559
00:35:23,947 --> 00:35:25,947
I think my sister tipped off a reporter.

560
00:35:27,007 --> 00:35:29,377
- Your sister? - I told her not to do it,

561
00:35:29,447 --> 00:35:31,347
but I guess she was angry thinking that it's unfair.

562
00:35:32,847 --> 00:35:35,007
Oh, I should get back inside.

563
00:35:35,007 --> 00:35:36,007
Okay.

564
00:35:39,547 --> 00:35:40,607
What is it?

565
00:35:42,507 --> 00:35:44,677
I was just thinking that she looks familiar for some reason.

566
00:35:47,947 --> 00:35:49,077
Now I know...

567
00:35:50,747 --> 00:35:52,107
whom she resembles.

568
00:35:54,107 --> 00:35:55,107
What do you mean?

569
00:35:55,347 --> 00:35:56,577
Who resembles whom?

570
00:35:56,577 --> 00:35:59,047
Ji Seok, let me ask a favor of you.

571
00:36:00,217 --> 00:36:01,217
What is it?

572
00:36:01,347 --> 00:36:02,807
Jo Sang Cheol.

573
00:36:03,347 --> 00:36:05,777
I want to know where his sister is now and what she's up to.

574
00:36:05,947 --> 00:36:07,077
Please find out.

575
00:36:07,407 --> 00:36:08,677
Jo Sang Cheol...

576
00:36:09,377 --> 00:36:12,217
Jo Sang Cheol is... He's that stalker, right?

577
00:36:12,547 --> 00:36:13,777
Why are you asking about his sister?

578
00:36:14,277 --> 00:36:16,307
There's something I'd like to check.

579
00:36:16,507 --> 00:36:17,577
As soon as possible.

580
00:36:19,647 --> 00:36:20,777
You made it.

581
00:36:21,277 --> 00:36:22,907
My place isn't nice, but please come in.

582
00:36:33,147 --> 00:36:34,277
Do you live alone?

583
00:36:35,647 --> 00:36:36,647
Yes.

584
00:36:37,177 --> 00:36:38,747
I had an older brother,

585
00:36:39,217 --> 00:36:40,717
but he died this year.

586
00:36:42,177 --> 00:36:44,507
Gosh, I'm sorry. I shouldn't have asked you that question.

587
00:36:44,577 --> 00:36:46,077
Don't worry. It's okay.

588
00:36:46,717 --> 00:36:48,277
I'm the one who should apologize.

589
00:36:48,607 --> 00:36:50,507
I'm asking a big favor of you out of the blue.

590
00:36:52,447 --> 00:36:53,847
Now that my brother is dead,

591
00:36:54,407 --> 00:36:55,907
Mimi is the only family...

592
00:36:56,607 --> 00:36:58,177
I have left.

593
00:37:02,177 --> 00:37:03,447
Don't cry.

594
00:37:03,847 --> 00:37:05,217
I'm sure it's nothing serious.

595
00:37:05,947 --> 00:37:08,107
By the way, where's Mimi?

596
00:37:09,277 --> 00:37:10,307
Over here.

597
00:37:14,217 --> 00:37:16,877
Mimi, you made me look like a liar.

598
00:37:17,007 --> 00:37:18,907
Why did you act like you were sick?

599
00:37:21,047 --> 00:37:22,447
That happens sometimes.

600
00:37:22,507 --> 00:37:23,947
Even when we're really ill,

601
00:37:23,947 --> 00:37:27,147
the pain can stop right in front of a hospital, you know.

602
00:37:28,447 --> 00:37:30,547
Anyway, I'm glad you're okay.

603
00:37:30,907 --> 00:37:31,907
I should get going.

604
00:37:32,377 --> 00:37:33,847
Wait, Seol.

605
00:37:35,507 --> 00:37:38,047
Stay for a drink since you came all the way here.

606
00:37:38,217 --> 00:37:40,007
I'll feel bad if I just let you go like this.

607
00:37:40,007 --> 00:37:42,747
Gosh, it's okay. I have to get going.

608
00:37:42,977 --> 00:37:45,847
Give me a second. I'll go bring something to drink.

609
00:38:01,847 --> 00:38:03,477
Do you like orange juice?

610
00:38:04,147 --> 00:38:05,147
Thanks.

611
00:38:06,007 --> 00:38:07,347
Drink it while it's still cold.

612
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,260
It's me.

613
00:38:43,600 --> 00:38:44,760
What's happening with Seol?

614
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:47,830
She must've been tired. She fell asleep.

615
00:38:47,830 --> 00:38:49,430
She's sleeping like a log.

616
00:38:50,530 --> 00:38:52,100
What should I do now?

617
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:54,160
Stay with her and keep a watchful eye on her.

618
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:56,900
Do not let her go until I tell you to do so.

619
00:38:57,230 --> 00:38:58,730
If you do that,

620
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:02,130
you'll get your hands on a big sum of money as I promised you.

621
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:04,760
You should let me in on the plan since we're in this together.

622
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:07,200
What in the world are you planning to do?

623
00:39:08,330 --> 00:39:09,700
You thought we're in this together?

624
00:39:09,970 --> 00:39:11,630
Don't be delusional.

625
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:14,560
I'm paying you.

626
00:39:14,560 --> 00:39:16,860
You just need to do exactly as I say.

627
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:18,970
I have to go.

628
00:39:27,330 --> 00:39:28,730
(Email has been sent.)

629
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:35,160
Hey, Seol. Why aren't you picking up?

630
00:39:36,230 --> 00:39:37,900
This is the third message I'm leaving in your voice mail.

631
00:39:42,130 --> 00:39:44,900
You're with that ghost right now, aren't you?

632
00:39:45,830 --> 00:39:46,930
Everything is okay, right?

633
00:39:48,600 --> 00:39:50,630
Call me as soon as you get this.

634
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:52,060
It's an order.

635
00:39:57,830 --> 00:39:58,900
Hold on.

636
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:02,900
(Sungsoocheong)

637
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:08,430
(Wang Bang Wool Fairy)

638
00:40:09,030 --> 00:40:10,100
Fairy...

639
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:18,730
Hello? This is the incredibly clairvoyant...

640
00:40:18,730 --> 00:40:21,030
Hello, this is Han Se Ju.

641
00:40:21,730 --> 00:40:22,970
Do you remember me?

642
00:40:23,060 --> 00:40:25,360
My goodness. Of course.

643
00:40:25,730 --> 00:40:26,760
I'm calling because...

644
00:40:27,100 --> 00:40:29,060
I can't get a hold of Seol at the moment.

645
00:40:29,060 --> 00:40:30,500
Is she there now by any chance?

646
00:40:30,530 --> 00:40:31,600
No, she isn't.

647
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:33,830
She did come by, but left after getting a phone call.

648
00:40:34,430 --> 00:40:35,430
Why do you ask?

649
00:40:36,160 --> 00:40:37,200
It's nothing.

650
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:41,130
If she comes back, please let her know that I'm waiting for her call.

651
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,660
Yes, thank you.

652
00:40:51,930 --> 00:40:52,970
Hey, Seol.

653
00:40:53,030 --> 00:40:54,130
I didn't want to believe it,

654
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:58,360
but can you not get a hold of Seol now by any chance?

655
00:40:59,970 --> 00:41:00,970
How...

656
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,060
How do you know?

657
00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:05,660
I sent you an email. Check that first.

658
00:41:22,530 --> 00:41:23,560
This is...

659
00:41:24,970 --> 00:41:26,660
What does this mean?

660
00:41:27,430 --> 00:41:28,800
What do you want from me?

661
00:41:28,930 --> 00:41:30,700
It's not like I'm calling you because I wanted to.

662
00:41:33,230 --> 00:41:35,860
Hadn't Seol's life been on the line,

663
00:41:35,970 --> 00:41:37,630
I wouldn't even have called you.

664
00:41:40,860 --> 00:41:43,130
Whose life is on the line?

665
00:41:43,470 --> 00:41:44,500
Jo Sang Mi.

666
00:41:44,970 --> 00:41:46,030
Age 22.

667
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:47,860
You must already know since you've read the email,

668
00:41:48,100 --> 00:41:49,700
but she's Jo Sang Cheol's sister.

669
00:41:50,230 --> 00:41:52,800
Thanks to her brother who knew everything about you,

670
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:56,400
she also learned about the sad story...

671
00:41:56,530 --> 00:41:58,500
behind the novel, "Fate".

672
00:41:58,830 --> 00:42:01,360
She's been using it to blackmail me,

673
00:42:02,860 --> 00:42:05,260
so I hired someone to dig up information on her.

674
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:08,730
Cut to the chase.

675
00:42:08,970 --> 00:42:10,900
Thanks to you, "Fate"...

676
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:13,630
made it into the trending keywords list once again today.

677
00:42:13,860 --> 00:42:16,260
That means Jo Sang Mi has lost her prey,

678
00:42:16,260 --> 00:42:18,930
but she called me again to threaten me with something else.

679
00:42:19,430 --> 00:42:21,900
Don't you understand the phrase, "Cut to the chase"?

680
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:27,130
She's holding Seol hostage.

681
00:42:28,330 --> 00:42:31,330
I don't know what she thinks my relationship with Seol is,

682
00:42:31,330 --> 00:42:32,470
but she threatened me.

683
00:42:32,700 --> 00:42:35,200
She told me to bring money if I want Seol to be alive.

684
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:38,030
But I don't think it's something I should take care of.

685
00:42:40,700 --> 00:42:41,900
Where are they now?

686
00:42:42,730 --> 00:42:43,800
I don't know either.

687
00:42:45,330 --> 00:42:47,760
But I'll forward you the address I received.

688
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:48,830
Try going there first.

689
00:42:49,700 --> 00:42:52,300
You must know very well since it's your area of expertise,

690
00:42:52,660 --> 00:42:53,730
but you should really try...

691
00:42:55,700 --> 00:42:57,400
not to provoke the kidnapper.

692
00:43:01,330 --> 00:43:03,030
If you want to protect Seol,

693
00:43:03,630 --> 00:43:04,800
you should keep this confidential...

694
00:43:05,960 --> 00:43:07,200
and go alone.

695
00:43:21,130 --> 00:43:22,430
This is fun.

696
00:43:23,730 --> 00:43:25,430
Mr. Han, I have an update for you.

697
00:43:26,030 --> 00:43:29,330
We looked into finding out more about the motorcycle terrorists...

698
00:43:29,330 --> 00:43:30,960
Do they have a connection with Jo Sang Mi?

699
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:32,530
How did you know...

700
00:43:33,060 --> 00:43:36,160
Oh, we also tracked down those guys who damaged the clip...

701
00:43:36,160 --> 00:43:37,160
By any chance,

702
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:40,630
is Tae Min affiliated with them?

703
00:43:40,960 --> 00:43:42,530
How did you know that?

704
00:43:43,100 --> 00:43:46,960
Anyway, the employee of the errand services who damaged the clip...

705
00:43:47,130 --> 00:43:49,960
said that Jo Sang Mi has been blackmailing Mr. Baek.

706
00:43:49,960 --> 00:43:53,960
Because of that, he hired them to tail her.

707
00:43:56,330 --> 00:43:59,330
Shall I ask the police to be on the lookout for Jo Sang Mi?

708
00:43:59,430 --> 00:44:01,500
No, please don't do anything yet.

709
00:44:01,900 --> 00:44:04,730
Instead, please stay here and be on call,

710
00:44:04,730 --> 00:44:06,830
so that I can get a hold of you whenever I need to.

711
00:44:08,730 --> 00:44:10,630
Mr. Han. Mr. Han!

712
00:45:09,330 --> 00:45:10,360
You came.

713
00:45:11,130 --> 00:45:12,500
Where is Seol?

714
00:45:13,700 --> 00:45:15,960
Where is she right now? You scum.

715
00:45:16,860 --> 00:45:17,900
I told you...

716
00:45:18,230 --> 00:45:20,030
not to provoke the kidnapper.

717
00:45:20,530 --> 00:45:22,230
If you keep this up,

718
00:45:22,430 --> 00:45:24,060
you won't be able to save the woman you love.

719
00:45:24,900 --> 00:45:26,300
I'm saying Seol...

720
00:45:26,600 --> 00:45:29,300
will die because of you, jerk.

721
00:45:29,760 --> 00:45:31,800
Were you behind Jo Sang Mi this whole time?

722
00:45:32,760 --> 00:45:33,960
"Kidnap her."

723
00:45:34,230 --> 00:45:36,400
"Hit her with the motorcycle."

724
00:45:37,600 --> 00:45:39,660
Were you behind everything all along?

725
00:45:40,800 --> 00:45:42,930
What kind of person do you think I am?

726
00:45:44,430 --> 00:45:47,500
Let me tell you exactly what's true and what's false.

727
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:51,200
The fact that Jo Sang Mi blackmailed me...

728
00:45:52,230 --> 00:45:53,230
is true.

729
00:45:54,130 --> 00:45:56,930
I told you that I don't know where Seol is.

730
00:46:00,800 --> 00:46:01,800
It was a lie.

731
00:46:06,630 --> 00:46:08,700
What are you trying to get by making me come here?

732
00:46:09,130 --> 00:46:11,430
I'll make sure you can accomplish your goal.

733
00:46:12,530 --> 00:46:14,630
First, tell me where Seol is now.

734
00:46:15,630 --> 00:46:17,630
This is what I thought as soon as I saw the article.

735
00:46:18,130 --> 00:46:19,400
"I should beg him."

736
00:46:19,630 --> 00:46:22,060
"I should ask him to take down the article and help me just this once."

737
00:46:24,130 --> 00:46:26,360
Then this thought suddenly popped up in my head.

738
00:46:27,600 --> 00:46:29,700
"No matter how desperately I beg him,"

739
00:46:30,360 --> 00:46:33,500
"he'll never do it for me."

740
00:46:34,900 --> 00:46:37,130
That's why things got this messed up.

741
00:46:38,530 --> 00:46:39,530
I'm saying...

742
00:46:40,730 --> 00:46:43,100
it's all your fault, you scum.

743
00:46:45,700 --> 00:46:46,730
Mr. Han.

744
00:46:47,160 --> 00:46:48,200
Seol.

745
00:46:48,430 --> 00:46:49,700
Is anybody here?

746
00:46:59,030 --> 00:47:02,100
Tell me where Seol is first.

747
00:47:02,100 --> 00:47:03,960
Why did you write about something so dangerous...

748
00:47:03,960 --> 00:47:06,130
and make someone take his own life?

749
00:47:06,360 --> 00:47:10,660
That young girl, Jo Sang Mi, is thirsty for revenge.

750
00:47:10,830 --> 00:47:14,060
I'm not sure if Seol would still be alive.

751
00:47:24,630 --> 00:47:26,300
When such cracks appear,

752
00:47:27,100 --> 00:47:29,460
your power starts to disperse little by little.

753
00:47:29,930 --> 00:47:32,400
If you continue to use your power and energy,

754
00:47:33,100 --> 00:47:35,260
the cracks will spread and deepen.

755
00:47:42,123 --> 00:47:43,123
The choice is yours.

756
00:47:43,953 --> 00:47:45,993
If you want to save Seol's life,

757
00:47:46,623 --> 00:47:48,593
you'll have to cover up the situation yourself.

758
00:47:49,093 --> 00:47:51,093
Call that piece of trash, Reporter Son,

759
00:47:51,093 --> 00:47:53,523
and tell him that the whole thing was staged by you.

760
00:47:54,893 --> 00:47:56,953
Then I'll tell you where Jo Sang Mi is.

761
00:47:58,523 --> 00:48:02,053
After kidnapping someone, you're harassing and even threatening me.

762
00:48:03,523 --> 00:48:05,523
How low are you willing to go?

763
00:48:06,593 --> 00:48:08,823
Don't you think you're at rock bottom now?

764
00:48:10,093 --> 00:48:11,323
Like I've already told you,

765
00:48:13,123 --> 00:48:15,523
that girl is capable of doing anything.

766
00:48:15,993 --> 00:48:18,123
I tamed her a little by offering her a large sum of money,

767
00:48:18,293 --> 00:48:19,793
but it's only a matter of time.

768
00:48:20,553 --> 00:48:22,523
No one can stop her now.

769
00:48:23,353 --> 00:48:25,123
No one knows what kind of ruse she'll cook up.

770
00:48:28,253 --> 00:48:31,053
I bet you're the one who cooked up all this, not her.

771
00:48:33,753 --> 00:48:37,223
- What? - Sure, she probably threatened you.

772
00:48:37,423 --> 00:48:42,053
But I'm sure you tied her down using the clip you obtained.

773
00:48:42,723 --> 00:48:46,793
Then the article came out unexpectedly.

774
00:48:47,453 --> 00:48:48,593
Make your choice.

775
00:48:49,093 --> 00:48:51,123
Do you want her to live or not?

776
00:48:51,123 --> 00:48:52,523
Let's see.

777
00:48:54,753 --> 00:48:58,123
Now that Jo Sang Mi's card is gone, what would you have done...

778
00:48:58,123 --> 00:48:59,823
had this been the only card you have?

779
00:49:02,053 --> 00:49:03,693
You'd probably have threatened her.

780
00:49:05,123 --> 00:49:07,023
I've sure you've spent quite a bit of money as well.

781
00:49:07,193 --> 00:49:08,253
That mouth.

782
00:49:11,653 --> 00:49:13,453
Shut it and make your choice.

783
00:49:34,023 --> 00:49:35,993
That girl, Jo Sang Mi,

784
00:49:36,593 --> 00:49:38,753
must be waiting for your call while holding Seol...

785
00:49:39,453 --> 00:49:41,353
captive somewhere.

786
00:49:41,793 --> 00:49:43,953
No, you're wrong.

787
00:49:44,623 --> 00:49:46,253
I'm the one who was threatened.

788
00:49:46,723 --> 00:49:49,823
All I did was make you come here, which she told me to do.

789
00:49:51,093 --> 00:49:53,053
The police will find out the truth.

790
00:50:01,153 --> 00:50:02,253
Ms. Kang.

791
00:50:03,023 --> 00:50:06,893
Please call the police immediately and ask them to find Jo Sang Mi.

792
00:50:12,123 --> 00:50:13,623
I'll save Seol's life on my own.

793
00:50:14,153 --> 00:50:15,753
I do not need your help.

794
00:50:26,793 --> 00:50:27,993
Let's just...

795
00:50:29,593 --> 00:50:31,793
Hey, what are you doing now?

796
00:50:33,493 --> 00:50:34,953
Let's just put an end to everything now.

797
00:50:35,253 --> 00:50:36,493
Have you lost your mind?

798
00:50:42,953 --> 00:50:44,023
I...

799
00:50:45,993 --> 00:50:47,693
I can't let you walk away like that.

800
00:50:48,353 --> 00:50:50,693
If you don't help me cover it up,

801
00:50:51,723 --> 00:50:55,523
this is the only choice I can make.

802
00:50:55,923 --> 00:50:57,023
Come down.

803
00:50:58,093 --> 00:50:59,593
Come down right now!

804
00:51:01,223 --> 00:51:02,223
No,

805
00:51:02,953 --> 00:51:04,253
I don't want to.

806
00:51:04,993 --> 00:51:06,053
I told you before.

807
00:51:06,623 --> 00:51:08,093
I'd much rather die.

808
00:51:09,123 --> 00:51:11,023
I cannot tolerate people looking at me...

809
00:51:12,993 --> 00:51:14,353
with utter contempt.

810
00:51:16,323 --> 00:51:17,623
I won't be able to stand it.

811
00:51:19,593 --> 00:51:20,593
I'm...

812
00:51:23,623 --> 00:51:25,053
exhausted, Se Ju.

813
00:51:32,593 --> 00:51:33,923
Hey, hey!

814
00:51:37,523 --> 00:51:39,893
Move. Don't block me, you jerk.

815
00:51:40,153 --> 00:51:41,193
Get out of my way!

816
00:51:42,223 --> 00:51:43,293
Hey, no!

817
00:51:44,293 --> 00:51:45,453
No!

818
00:51:45,623 --> 00:51:47,553
- Let go. - No.

819
00:51:47,553 --> 00:51:49,953
- No! - Let go. Let go!

820
00:51:50,593 --> 00:51:51,623
Let go of me!

821
00:52:11,093 --> 00:52:15,153
I'm sure the two of you will have a great time.

822
00:52:20,393 --> 00:52:22,353
- Drink up. - Cheers.

823
00:53:17,523 --> 00:53:18,853
You two made it.

824
00:53:19,153 --> 00:53:22,123
My gosh. I love the ambiance at this party, Young Min.

825
00:53:22,953 --> 00:53:25,523
I must say, you look dashing today, Yul.

826
00:53:26,153 --> 00:53:28,593
I bought this suit at Mitsukoshi for tonight.

827
00:53:30,393 --> 00:53:33,323
Thank you for inviting me. I'm not even a fitting guest.

828
00:53:33,823 --> 00:53:36,223
That's not true at all. You should be invited, of course.

829
00:53:37,353 --> 00:53:38,953
I'm sure the two of you...

830
00:53:40,823 --> 00:53:42,823
will have a great time tonight.

831
00:53:44,223 --> 00:53:45,353
I'm looking forward to it.

832
00:53:46,153 --> 00:53:48,323
I'm already having a great time.

833
00:53:53,823 --> 00:53:56,553
I have to excuse myself to greet other guests. Sorry.

834
00:54:00,825 --> 00:54:02,895
The final goal of our mission today...

835
00:54:03,295 --> 00:54:06,725
is achieving two objectives through a feint operation.

836
00:54:07,655 --> 00:54:09,525
- Cheers. - Cheers.

837
00:54:09,725 --> 00:54:11,795
Expecting Joseon Youth Alliance's attack, they will...

838
00:54:12,055 --> 00:54:15,755
make sure the entire police force guards the area around the venue.

839
00:54:16,555 --> 00:54:20,155
We'll use that situation to our advantage.

840
00:54:20,555 --> 00:54:24,355
They look as if they've received a gift, not caught in a trap.

841
00:54:44,825 --> 00:54:46,855
While all of their eyes and ears...

842
00:54:46,855 --> 00:54:50,155
are focused on the party venue where the high-up officials are,

843
00:54:50,155 --> 00:54:53,355
Team 2 and 3 who are hiding in Hwanggeumjeong will start moving...

844
00:54:53,755 --> 00:54:57,955
to throw bombs at Siksan Bank and Oriental Development Company...

845
00:54:57,955 --> 00:55:00,355
which have been aiding Japan in their brutal colonization of Joseon.

846
00:55:00,695 --> 00:55:02,895
Then it'll turn into a street battle,

847
00:55:03,425 --> 00:55:06,055
and we'll distribute the Declaration of Joseon's Independence...

848
00:55:06,155 --> 00:55:07,925
to let the world know of our determination.

849
00:55:08,655 --> 00:55:10,055
That's our first goal.

850
00:55:20,155 --> 00:55:21,425
What happened?

851
00:55:21,425 --> 00:55:24,495
There were bombings at Siksan Bank and Oriental Development Company.

852
00:55:24,625 --> 00:55:26,925
Who did it? Did you guys catch the culprit?

853
00:55:27,225 --> 00:55:29,895
It looks like it was done by an organization.

854
00:55:29,895 --> 00:55:31,425
They're distributing propaganda flyers...

855
00:55:31,425 --> 00:55:33,455
while causing a street battle and running away at the same time.

856
00:55:34,055 --> 00:55:35,195
Is it Joseon Youth Alliance?

857
00:55:35,195 --> 00:55:36,895
Send the police force there immediately.

858
00:55:38,025 --> 00:55:40,395
Capture every one of them without an exception.

859
00:55:40,495 --> 00:55:42,995
If anyone resists, you can shoot him on the spot.

860
00:55:43,995 --> 00:55:46,395
Why are you just standing there? Go sort it out right now!

861
00:55:46,755 --> 00:55:47,925
- Yes, sir! - Yes, sir.

862
00:55:48,755 --> 00:55:52,425
You should prepare yourself for the consequences of this.

863
00:55:56,125 --> 00:55:58,925
Once the police force starts moving towards Hwanggeumjeong,

864
00:55:59,295 --> 00:56:02,325
Team One on site will infiltrate into the banquet venue.

865
00:56:02,425 --> 00:56:05,625
We'll steal the money donated for war fund for our rebel forces.

866
00:56:05,725 --> 00:56:10,155
Then we'll assassinate all the pro-Japan authorities...

867
00:56:10,355 --> 00:56:11,795
and the leading members of their military.

868
00:56:12,695 --> 00:56:14,525
That's our second goal.

869
00:56:17,225 --> 00:56:21,125
Those who are disguised as catering staffs will...

870
00:56:21,195 --> 00:56:24,195
sneak the weapons into the venue along with food ingredients.

871
00:56:25,455 --> 00:56:28,755
Those of you who are disguised as the high-up officials' entourage...

872
00:56:28,755 --> 00:56:32,525
will have to take care of their real entourage in advance.

873
00:56:34,355 --> 00:56:35,525
And...

874
00:56:37,395 --> 00:56:38,625
our comrade, Su Hyeon,

875
00:56:40,325 --> 00:56:42,855
will kick-start our key mission.

876
00:57:58,395 --> 00:58:01,595
Did they know what time the bombs would go off?

877
00:58:03,025 --> 00:58:05,055
Stop. Stop!

878
00:58:36,195 --> 00:58:37,255
What's going on?

879
00:58:37,525 --> 00:58:39,495
- Why did the lights go off? - What's happening?

880
00:58:40,095 --> 00:58:41,555
- What is this? - What's going on?

881
00:58:41,555 --> 00:58:43,255
- What is happening? - Why did the lights turn off?

882
00:58:55,925 --> 00:58:57,495
- My gosh! - The lights...

883
00:59:03,295 --> 00:59:04,995
As a member of Joseon Youth Alliance,

884
00:59:05,325 --> 00:59:07,795
I hereby announce that we'll keep fighting for Joseon's independence,

885
00:59:07,995 --> 00:59:10,125
and that we will assassinate those who are in the way...

886
00:59:10,525 --> 00:59:11,755
of our country's independence.

887
00:59:56,495 --> 00:59:59,295
(Chicago Typewriter)

888
00:59:59,295 --> 01:00:01,725
If we meet again in our next lives,

889
01:00:01,825 --> 01:00:03,925
please think of me as a woman.

890
01:00:03,955 --> 01:00:06,095
In the next life, give her up.

891
01:00:06,255 --> 01:00:08,395
Remember what you promised me in the past life?

892
01:00:08,395 --> 01:00:10,225
How much more can I express myself?

893
01:00:10,455 --> 01:00:12,555
And you two should talk casually to each other from now on.

894
01:00:12,555 --> 01:00:14,355
You've been friends for over 80 years.

895
01:00:14,355 --> 01:00:16,225
Better yet, he should be serving me like his master.

896
01:00:16,225 --> 01:00:17,725
But I beg to differ, my dear friend.

897
01:00:17,725 --> 01:00:19,495
- Do you want to die? - I'm already dead.

898
01:00:19,495 --> 01:00:21,895
From this moment, we're changing the plan.

899
01:00:21,895 --> 01:00:22,895
Boss.

900
01:00:23,055 --> 01:00:25,825
Su Hyeon, you must come back in one piece.

901
01:00:26,784 --> 01:00:28,014
It's an order.
